19template <typename Next>
20class SimplifiedLoweringReducer : public Next {
21 public:
22 TURBOSHAFT_REDUCER_BOILERPLATE(SimplifiedLowering)
23
24 using Rep = RegisterRepresentation;
25
26 enum class CheckKind {
27 kNone,
28 kSigned32,
29 };
30
31 OpIndex REDUCE_INPUT_GRAPH(SpeculativeNumberBinop)(
32 OpIndex ig_index, const SpeculativeNumberBinopOp& op) {
33 DCHECK_EQ(op.kind, SpeculativeNumberBinopOp::Kind::kSafeIntegerAdd);
34
35 OpIndex frame_state = Map(op.frame_state());
36 V<Word32> left = ProcessInput(Map(op.left()), Rep::Word32(),
37 CheckKind::kSigned32, frame_state);
38 V<Word32> right = ProcessInput(Map(op.right()), Rep::Word32(),
39 CheckKind::kSigned32, frame_state);
40
41 V<Tuple<Word32, Word32>> result = __ Int32AddCheckOverflow(left, right);
42
43 V<Word32> overflow = __ template Projection<1>(result);
44 __ DeoptimizeIf(overflow, Map(op.frame_state()),
45 DeoptimizeReason::kOverflow, FeedbackSource{});
46 return __ template Projection<0>(result);
47 }
48
49 OpIndex REDUCE_INPUT_GRAPH(Return)(OpIndex ig_index, const ReturnOp& ret) {
50 base::SmallVector<OpIndex, 8> return_values;
51 for (OpIndex input : ret.return_values()) {
52 return_values.push_back(
53 ProcessInput(Map(input), Rep::Tagged(), CheckKind::kNone, {}));
54 }
55
56 __ Return(Map(ret.pop_count()), base::VectorOf(return_values));
57 return OpIndex::Invalid();
58 }
59
60 OpIndex ProcessInput(OpIndex input_index, RegisterRepresentation target_rep,
61 CheckKind type_check, OptionalOpIndex frame_state) {
62 const Operation& input_op = __ output_graph().Get(input_index);
63 DCHECK_EQ(input_op.outputs_rep().size(), 1);
64
65 RegisterRepresentation output_rep = input_op.outputs_rep()[0];
66 if (output_rep == target_rep && type_check == CheckKind::kNone) {
67 return input_index;
68 }
69
70 switch (multi(output_rep, target_rep)) {
71 case multi(Rep::Tagged(), Rep::Word32()): {
72 // TODO(nicohartmann@): More cases.
73 DCHECK_EQ(type_check, CheckKind::kSigned32);
74 return __ ConvertJSPrimitiveToUntaggedOrDeopt(
75 input_index, frame_state.value(),
76 ConvertJSPrimitiveToUntaggedOrDeoptOp::JSPrimitiveKind::kNumber,
77 ConvertJSPrimitiveToUntaggedOrDeoptOp::UntaggedKind::kInt32,
78 CheckForMinusZeroMode::kCheckForMinusZero, {});
79 }
80 case multi(Rep::Word32(), Rep::Tagged()): {
81 // TODO(nicohartmann@): More cases.
82 return __ ConvertUntaggedToJSPrimitive(
83 input_index,
84 ConvertUntaggedToJSPrimitiveOp::JSPrimitiveKind::kNumber,
85 Rep::Word32(),
86 ConvertUntaggedToJSPrimitiveOp::InputInterpretation::kSigned,
87 CheckForMinusZeroMode::kDontCheckForMinusZero);
88 }
89
90 default:
91 UNIMPLEMENTED();
92 }
93 }
94
95 inline OpIndex Map(OpIndex ig_index) { return __ MapToNewGraph(ig_index); }
96};
